| **04h** | 0 | 日 | [cite_start]01–31 [cite: 484] |
| **05h** | Century | 月 / 世紀 | [cite_start]01–12 + 世紀 [cite: 484, 508] |
| **06h** | — | 年 | [cite_start]00–99 [cite: 484] |
